1
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:23,630
One, two.

2
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:36,580
Sorry about that.

3
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:40,250
I just wanted
to do a little cleaning.

4
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,170
The poverty filth
in this school.

5
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:55,380
Oh, my.

6
00:00:55,630 --> 00:00:56,880
A shoe locker.

7
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:58,460
Being used as a trash can?

8
00:00:58,500 --> 00:00:59,790
How creative!

9
00:01:03,330 --> 00:01:04,960
We're not done
talking, are we?

10
00:01:05,170 --> 00:01:06,670
I have nothing to say.

11
00:01:06,830 --> 00:01:08,210
If I say we're talking,
we're talking.

12
00:01:08,210 --> 00:01:09,630
Don't get so cocky,
you poor thing.

13
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:11,460
You're just a poor kid from a single-parent home.

14
00:01:11,670 --> 00:01:13,290
You think you can just
casually talk to her?

15
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:14,710
Don't you get it?

16
00:01:14,750 --> 00:01:16,290
Alright, alright.
That's enough.

17
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:17,630
See? Everything's fine now.

18
00:01:17,750 --> 00:01:19,540
Just because Makishima-san
spoke to you a few times.

19
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:20,580
You got all full of yourself.

20
00:01:20,790 --> 00:01:21,790
Don't push your luck.

21
00:01:22,250 --> 00:01:23,500
Stay away from her.

22
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,250
The Invincible Lord of the Universe
is coming!

23
00:01:34,750 --> 00:01:35,750
Huh?
